data.description: Less than 6 miles from Blue Oval! Welcome To the Country. Adorable Farmhouse with 3 beds and 2.5 baths sits on 2.87Ac. Come sit on the front porch and enjoy the sunset or the side porch swing for the sunrise. All the comforts of home. Comes with Refrigerator, washer and Dryer. Open Kitchen / Dining area. Comfortable Den. Attached Covered parking. Great Big Metal Work Shop or Storage space in the backyard. And Guess what? This home could also be used as a AirB&B. Don't miss your chance!
